    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You take a large gulp from a moderate jug of heroes water. <br />This water magnifies its abilities to that of unprecedented figures. <br />You gain a +4 bonus to All ability scores for the next minute, but in exchange for this power, you automatically, reduce your current and maximum hit points by an amount equal to 50% of your maximum hit points. <br />This hit point reduction ignores health gates if you are a Solo.</p>",
